videos.headline: Missouri catches early pick-6
videos.description: Christian Holmes returns an interception thrown by Brady White for 42 yards to give Missouri a 14-0 lead over Memphis.

videos.headline: Memphis fighting their way back after 30-yard TD catch
videos.description: Brady White connects with Tony Pollard for a 30-yard catch and a score to cut Missouri's lead to 21-17.

videos.headline: Lock throws his third TD of  first half
videos.description: Drew Lock hooks up with Albert Okwuegbunam for a 47-yard score to give Missouri a 48-20 lead over Memphis in the first half.

videos.headline: Rountree III breaks loose for a 59-yard score
videos.description: Larry Rountree III runs for a 59-yard score.
